casebody.data:
No. 67,

Orig.

Idaho ex rel. Andrus, Governor of Idaho, et al. v. Oregon et al. [For earlier order herein, see 423 U. S. 813.]

Motion of Izaak Walton League of America, Inc., et al. for leave to file brief as amici curiae granted. Motion for leave to file bill of complaint set for oral argument in due course.
